{"title":"铁算盘","authors":["彭德林"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":4,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁算盘（快板）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖北高飞一大队  彭德林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁算盘，一尺三，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日夜不离我身边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我打算盘忆往事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新旧社会两重天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧社会，真黑暗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万恶地主掌算盘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"算盘一打滴嗒响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"算尽穷人血和汗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四九年，换新天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷人夺回铁算盘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我拿算盘上学校，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化技术学得全。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"集体化，日子甜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫农的儿子掌算盘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年丰收把账算，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃穿有余笑开颜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁算盘，一尺三，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日夜不离我身边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧握算盘跟党走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命二字记心间。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}